<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-+0n0xVW2eSR5OomGNYDnhzAbDsOXxcvSN1TPprVMTNDbiYZCxYbOOl7+AMvyTG2x" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,400;0,600;1,100&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">

    <title>Welcome to <%= store.name %>
    </title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <main>
        <div class="container py-4">
            <header class="pb-3 mb-4 border-bottom">
                <a class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between text-dark text-decoration-none">
                    <img src="../image/droppa_icon.jpg" alt="" class="rounded" style="max-width: 3rem;">
                    <span class="fs-4">
                        <%= store.email %>
                    </span>
                </a>
            </header>

            <div class="p-5 mb-4 bg-light rounded-3">
                <div class="container-fluid py-5">

                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between text-dark text-decoration-none">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <h1 class="display-6 fw-light">Welcome <%= store.name %>
                                </h1>

                                <p class="col-md-12 fs-5 fw-light">You have successfully activated Droppa Shipping App
                                    on your store. You can now navigate to your online store and use the app.</p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <h1 class="lead fw-light fw-bold">Your Store Information
                                </h1>

                                <% if (store !=="" ) { %>
                                    <ul class="list-group fs-6 fw-light">
                                        <li class="list-group-item">Store Name: <%= store.domain %>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="list-group-item">Address: <%= store.address1 %>, <%= store.zip %>,
                                                    <%= store.city %>, <%= store.province %>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="list-group-item">Email Address: <%= store.email %>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <% } %>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row align-items-md-stretch">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="h-100 p-5 text-white bg-dark rounded-3">
                        <h2 class="fw-bold" style="color: #179fd6;">Droppa For Businesses</h2>
                        <p class="col-md-12 fs-5 fw-light">A gateway for retail stores and businesses to
                            book and manage
                            deliveries on
                            behalf of their customers using a shipping app.</p>

                        <p class="col-md-12 fs-5 fw-light">Retailers can now register with Droppa and have
                            this value
                            added to their supply chain. Droppa Retail booking system can be integrated with
                            any
                            e-commerce store or business and managed remotely.</p>

                        <a href="https://www.droppa.co.za/droppa/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-primary"
                            type="button">Read more</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="h-100 p-5 bg-light border rounded-3">
                        <h2 style="color: #179fd6;" class="fw-bold">What Droppa Offers</h2>
                        <p>Courier is an active customer support system dedicated to providing our clients
                            with
                            effective and convenient logistics solutions.</p>

                        <ul>
                            <li> Dash is the same day delivery that only operates within Brookyln & Sandton
                                radius.</li>
                            <li> Flash flight - same day delivery via GAU, WCT & KZN.</li>
                            <li> Flash On Road - same day delivery service.</li>
                            <li> Express Courier - 1 to 3 working days.</li>
                            <li> Budget Courier - 2 to 5 working days</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <footer class="pt-3 mt-4 text-muted border-top">

            </footer>
        </div>
    </main>

</body>

</html>